{"tid":1558542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抵制黨鐵新戰線！","createTime":"2019-09-10T13:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T02:20:12.000Z","uid":144018,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"881983be5b815a271096d78d1833086be2693962","tid":1558542,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:27:01.000Z","msg":"2019年7月21日<br />\n2019年8月31日<br />\n兩個故係香港人都唔會忘記既日子，因為短短一個月內黨鐵站先後發生咗兩單恐怖襲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黨鐵係公共交通工具市場佔有率接近5成，係市民同旅客出入主要既交通工具之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係黨鐵內發生咁大件事，當然要話俾旅客聽等佢哋嚟香港旅遊嗰陣多多小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講唔知原來昂坪360係黨鐵既附屬公司嚟，而昂坪360又係好受歡迎既景點，好多旅客嚟香港都會專程去坐下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然係咁我哋好應該去昂坪360既Page貼返啲資訊，提提旅客們去搭黨鐵／昂坪360時要多多小心，唔係一個唔覺意有班蒙面恐怖份子衝上車無差別咁打人就唔係咁好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旅客Connected！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70651200_2528918517384769_1166959472069836800_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_oc=AQmRPXkwg9LjYWQ9yw0VfIGze-5h2V3ocj54E1YBltupb0IQ4DEyc6WKIxiuo8uZbXE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=ff094973dfd3c0d217ff727088de8fe5&amp;oe=5DF7E215\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70651200_2528918517384769_1166959472069836800_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_oc%3DAQmRPXkwg9LjYWQ9yw0VfIGze-5h2V3ocj54E1YBltupb0IQ4DEyc6WKIxiuo8uZbXE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dff094973dfd3c0d217ff727088de8fe5%26oe%3D5DF7E215&h=a9cbbdac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95dae5e4a53ecf5797618957a30435a346ef68eb","tid":1558542,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b23f5dffaa76b16115ef179fbf9e27809517c37","tid":1558542,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:34:31.000Z","msg":"自推十連一"},{"pid":"af68180e1b2326e826c94699e3229ed5305e7dd9","tid":1558542,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:34:42.000Z","msg":"自推十連二"},{"pid":"461b3b5f99014b937d48699c0c0f5fd0af31b49d","tid":1558542,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"自推十連三"},{"pid":"11e280650e818c16823394e19d1db4d01694d5d0","tid":1558542,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"自推十連四"},{"pid":"ebd0b7bfe17ff09201345a695859116e9088cb08","tid":1558542,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"自推十連五"},{"pid":"204a7df66496b74ff885090820916d2424b9d226","tid":1558542,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:35:23.000Z","msg":"自推十連六"},{"pid":"b22c8b02b59037b4ef0af48cee6eaedb2c2749e6","tid":1558542,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:35:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfc4e62efa99f64ba9da1b3dda01d197538ff082","tid":1558542,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime